<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> Central body </inglise>
<eesti> Keskasutus </eesti>
<inglise> In order to enable transmitting and receiving agencies to resolve difficulties arising from implementation of the Convention which cannot be resolved through contacts at agency level, the Convention has provided for central bodies to be set up to solve such problems via direct contacts between the transmitting agency and the central body of the State addressed. </inglise>
