<inglise> Under point (a) a transmitting agency may seek information from the central body of another State. </inglise>
<eesti> Punkti a kohaselt v&otilde;ib edastav asutus taotleda teise riigi keskasutuselt teavet. </eesti>
<inglise> A transmitting agency lacking the requisite information may need to enquire, for example, as to which receiving agency a given document has to be sent to for service. </inglise>
