<inglise> Point (b) may relate to specific cases or to more general difficulties. </inglise>
<eesti> Punkt b v&otilde;ib seonduda konkreetsete juhtude v&otilde;i &uuml;ldisemate probleemidega. </eesti>
<inglise> A transmitting agency will be able to seek the help of another Member State's central body if some time has elapsed since it sent a document to that Member State's receiving agency but a number of requests for information have filed to establish what action was taken after the document's transmission. </inglise>
