<inglise> If the applicant chooses to have the document translated, he will have to pay the cost of translation in advance; however, this rule does not preclude any subsequent ruling on costs enabling the applicant to be reimbursed for all or part of the expenditure he has incurred, if the law of the Member State in which the proceedings take place so provides. </inglise>
